snippet.title: Bionic Bay  -  Official Demo Trailer  -  Available Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Demo version of Bionic Bay is now available on Steam: https://bit.ly/3zfJswc

Bionic Bay is a unique physics based Sci-Fi platformer with action, creative game mechanics and a mysterious world crafted with exceptional detail.

https://twitter.com/BionicBay
https://discord.gg/A8pXbEqv2g
